Definition: without hope because there seems to be no possibility of comfort or success
Example: in an agony of hopeless grief; with a hopeless sigh he sat down
Synonyms: noun, feeling, hopelessness, HOPEFUL, DISCOURAGING, IMPOSSIBLE, PESSIMISTIC, without, hope, because, there, seems, to, be, no, possibility, of, comfort, or, success, in, an, agony, hopeless, grief, with, a, sigh, he, sat, down
Category: adj.all
